00:47:23.240 --> 00:47:23.560
we go.

00:47:24.100 --> 00:47:25.640
Bear type brings Rust C++

00:47:25.640 --> 00:47:26.780
inspired zero cost

00:47:26.780 --> 00:47:27.860
abstractions into the

00:47:27.860 --> 00:47:29.400
